    <div class="card">
      <h3>Download / Release</h3>
      <p class="lead">Get a packaged release from GitHub Releases (APK, App Bundle, Web).</p>
      <p><a href="https://github.com/cmwen/min-android-app-template/releases/latest" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--accent);text-decoration:none">Download latest release â†’</a></p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
