      <p class="lead">Get started in minutes with Flutter.</p>
      <pre style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.02);padding:10px;border-radius:8px;margin-top:8px;overflow:auto">git clone https://github.com/cmwen/min-android-app-template.git
cd min-android-app-template
flutter pub get
flutter run</pre>
      <p style="margin-top:8px"><a href="/install" style="color:var(--accent);text-decoration:none">Open full install guide â†’</a></p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>Next steps</h3>
      <ol>
        <li>Customize <code>lib/main.dart</code> with your app</li>
        <li>Update <code>pubspec.yaml</code> with your app name</li>
        <li>Configure <code>astro/astro.config.mjs</code> for your GitHub Pages URL</li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
